25#ifndef __EVERGREEN_SMC_H__
26#define __EVERGREEN_SMC_H__
27
28#include "rv770_smc.h"
29
30#pragma pack(push, 1)
31
32#define SMC_EVERGREEN_MC_REGISTER_ARRAY_SIZE 16
33
34struct SMC_Evergreen_MCRegisterAddress
35{
36 uint16_t s0;
37 uint16_t s1;
38};
39
40typedef struct SMC_Evergreen_MCRegisterAddress SMC_Evergreen_MCRegisterAddress;
41
42
43struct SMC_Evergreen_MCRegisterSet
44{
45 uint32_t value[SMC_EVERGREEN_MC_REGISTER_ARRAY_SIZE];
46};
47
48typedef struct SMC_Evergreen_MCRegisterSet SMC_Evergreen_MCRegisterSet;
49
50struct SMC_Evergreen_MCRegisters
51{
52 uint8_t last;
53 uint8_t reserved[3];
54 SMC_Evergreen_MCRegisterAddress address[SMC_EVERGREEN_MC_REGISTER_ARRAY_SIZE];
55 SMC_Evergreen_MCRegisterSet data[5];
56};
57
58typedef struct SMC_Evergreen_MCRegisters SMC_Evergreen_MCRegisters;
59
60#define EVERGREEN_SMC_FIRMWARE_HEADER_LOCATION 0x100
61
62#define EVERGREEN_SMC_FIRMWARE_HEADER_softRegisters 0x8
63#define EVERGREEN_SMC_FIRMWARE_HEADER_stateTable 0xC
64#define EVERGREEN_SMC_FIRMWARE_HEADER_mcRegisterTable 0x20
65
66
67#pragma pack(pop)
68
69#endif
